June 16,2025
-----------
* Edited the older version of `fmt::format` to work with new version of fmt by making format-strings runtime based
* fmt currently uses two types of format strings, 1. Run Time based/dynamic  2.
Compile Time Base/Static.
* Wrapped every dynamic format string in `fmt::runtime()` solved the building
issue.
